    <innerclass refid="classADS1115" prot="public">ADS1115</innerclass>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Thin wrapper over Adafruit_ADS1115 that provides a forward-declarable class name. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="PinRef_8h" kindref="compound">PinRef.h</ref> forward-declares <computeroutput>class <ref refid="classADS1115" kindref="compound">ADS1115</ref></computeroutput>. A typedef alias cannot be forward-declared with <computeroutput>class</computeroutput>, so this file defines a concrete wrapper class that inherits every constructor and method from Adafruit_ADS1115 without adding any logic.</para>
<para>Adafruit_ADS1115 takes address and bus via begin(), not the constructor. Pattern: <ref refid="classADS1115" kindref="compound">ADS1115</ref> adc; PanelGroup::registerADC(adc, 0x48, Wire);</para>
<para><simplesect kind="version"><para>0.1.0 </para>
</simplesect>
